      <title>朝鲜领导人金正恩妹妹：我们将建立压倒性的军事力量</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-leader-kims-sister-we-will-build-overwhelming-military-power-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据朝鲜朝中社周三报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩的妹妹金与正表示，朝鲜将继续建设压倒性的、最强大的军事力量，以保护其主权和地区和平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-leader-kims-sister-we-will-build-overwhelming-military-power-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 21:44:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：电子邮件显示，美国国防承包商 L3Harris 将裁员 5% 以节省成本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-defense-contractor-l3harris-cut-5-workforce-save-costs-email-shows-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社周二看到的美国国防承包商 L3Harris Technologies Inc. 首席执行官克里斯·库巴斯克 (Chris Kubasik) 在发给员工的电子邮件中表示，作为节省成本措施的一部分，今年将裁员 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-defense-contractor-l3harris-cut-5-workforce-save-costs-email-shows-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 18:59:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗威胁称，如果以色列发动重大袭击，将消灭以色列</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-threatens-annihilate-israel-should-it-launch-major-attack-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗官方通讯社援引伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西周二的话说，以色列对伊朗领土的袭击可能会从根本上改变局势，并导致“犹太复国主义政权”不复存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-threatens-annihilate-israel-should-it-launch-major-attack-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 14:19:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>不稳定的核废料坝威胁着肥沃的中亚腹地</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/unstable-nuclear-waste-dams-threaten-fertile-central-asia-heartland-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[研究显示，中亚肥沃的费尔干纳山谷上方储存着大量铀矿尾矿的水坝不稳定，如果它们倒塌，可能会引发切尔诺贝利规模的核灾难，导致该地区无法居住。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/unstable-nuclear-waste-dams-threaten-fertile-central-asia-heartland-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 13:24:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度竞选策略改变，莫迪称竞争对手支持穆斯林</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-calls-rivals-pro-muslim-election-campaign-changes-tack-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪和他的印度教民族主义政党已开始攻击反对派竞争对手，称他们支持穆斯林少数民族，分析人士认为这是为了在上周大选开始后重振他们的强硬派基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-calls-rivals-pro-muslim-election-campaign-changes-tack-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 11:05:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国将取代军方任命的参议院并减少其权力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-replace-military-appointed-senate-reduce-its-powers-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国内阁周二批准了一项选举新参议员名单的计划，这些参议员将不再被允许投票决定谁将成为总理，从而取消了强大的军方对谁领导国家的有效否决权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-replace-military-appointed-senate-reduce-its-powers-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:49:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：消息人士称，中国加大了地方政府债务跨境投资的力度</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-turns-heat-up-cross-border-investments-local-govt-debt-sources-say-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名消息人士称，中国监管机构正在检查利用跨境机制投资负债累累的地方政府的离岸债券，这表明中国监管机构正在加大力度遏制监管松散的市场部分的金融风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-turns-heat-up-cross-border-investments-local-govt-debt-sources-say-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:22:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国会准备通过乌克兰援助，武器即将推出</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/long-awaited-aid-ukraine-israel-taiwan-poised-pass-us-congress-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，针对乌克兰、以色列和台湾的数十亿美元对外援助在美国参议院取得进展，众议院上周突然结束了长达数月的僵局并批准了援助，随后将进行最终投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/long-awaited-aid-ukraine-israel-taiwan-poised-pass-us-congress-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:06:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通中国任命新任中国证券部门负责人</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-china-names-new-heads-china-investment-banking-arm-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通根据路透查阅并经公司发言人证实的公司备忘录，公司任命陆方为其中国证券部门董事会主席，接替前任董事长朴朴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-china-names-new-heads-china-investment-banking-arm-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 08:58:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
